  <goal>
    All R4 code changes deployed to dev environment:
    (1) Sprk.Bff.Api → Azure App Service (A-4 chat cap, B-4 modifiedOn, B-5 PUT+ETag, 044 webhook rename, 070 test-infra cleanup)
    (2) SpaarkeAi Code Page (W-3, W-4 DocumentViewer, W-5 SemanticSearchCriteriaTool, B-3 telemetry, 031 tab persistence, 042/043/044 widget/dialog, C-3, C-4 + add-on tasks 072/073/074/075)
    (3) LegalWorkspace web resource (044 SmartToDoDialog inline modal)
    (4) CalendarSidePane (B-6 CalendarFilterPane + UTC fix + 076 shape migration)
    (5) EventsPage (B-7 + B-8 + 067 + 074)

    Smoke each deploy. Document successful smoke results in `notes/079-deploy-verification.md`.
