  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Pre-flight">Verify working tree clean. Verify all task POMLs are status=completed for 072–078. Verify last commit pushed.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Build verify">Run BFF + each Code Page build. All 0 errors. (BFF + SpaarkeAi + LegalWorkspace + CalendarSidePane + EventsPage)</step>
    <step order="3" name="BFF publish size check">`dotnet publish -c Release src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ -o deploy/api-publish/`. Verify compressed size ≤60 MB. Document size.</step>
    <step order="4" name="BFF CVE check">`dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive`. No new HIGH-severity. Document any findings.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Operator gate: BFF deploy approval">Pause. Present BFF deploy plan + sizes + CVE check. Wait for operator approval before deploying BFF.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Deploy BFF">Invoke `bff-deploy` skill. Target: dev environment. Capture deploy output + URL.</step>
    <step order="7" name="BFF smoke">Hit `/healthz`. Hit `/api/workspace/layouts` (verify modifiedOn in response). PUT a layout with stale ETag (verify 412). Chat with a 20 MB attachment (verify accepted, 26 MB rejected). Document.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Operator gate: Code Page deploys">Pause. Confirm BFF smoke green. Get operator approval to proceed with Code Page deploys.</step>
    <step order="9" name="Deploy SpaarkeAi">Invoke `code-page-deploy` skill for `sprk_spaarkeai`. Smoke: cold load, create workspace tab, mount via Assistant (W-4), mount via Context (W-5), reload to verify tab persists (031), dark mode toggle.</step>
    <step order="10" name="Deploy LegalWorkspace">Invoke `code-page-deploy` skill for `sprk_corporateworkspace` (legacy name) OR appropriate LegalWorkspace web resource. Smoke: open SmartToDoDialog from Matter form (044), verify inline render (not iframe).</step>
    <step order="11" name="Deploy CalendarSidePane">Invoke `code-page-deploy` skill. Smoke: open side pane, filter by date range across DST boundary, verify Apply works, verify no UTC drift on filter dates.</step>
    <step order="12" name="Deploy EventsPage">Invoke `code-page-deploy` skill. Smoke: open page, exercise bulk actions (B-7), verify Calendar widget renders correctly with rich badges (064 + 067).</step>
    <step order="13" name="Final verification">Run full smoke checklist from `docs/guides/DEPLOYMENT-VERIFICATION-GUIDE.md` on SpaarkeAi.</step>
    <step order="14" name="Document">Write `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r4/notes/079-deploy-verification.md` with: each deploy's URL/version, smoke results, BFF publish size, any anomalies, sign-off.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Bash">dotnet publish, dotnet list package, git status, npm run build</tool>
    <tool name="Read">Inspect deploy outputs</tool>
    <tool name="Skill">bff-deploy, code-page-deploy</tool>
  </tools>

